Brugada Syndrome and Early Repolarisation Syndrome Avoidance of fever, including the use of anti-pyretics and avoidance of drugs that precipitate arrhythmia and type 1 ECG change, is the mainstay of treatment in Brugada syndrome (brugadadrugs.org).47

